Global Granular Molding Compound(GMC) Market Insights
Granular Molding Compound(GMC) Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Granular Molding Compound(GMC) Market Overview
The Granular Molding Compound (GMC) market is projected to witness significant growth, reaching an estimated market value of $5.8 billion by 2028, expanding at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of approximately 4.5% during the forecast period. This growth is attributed to the increasing demand for precision and efficiency in manufacturing industries, including automotive, electrical, and electronics. GMC is widely used in the production of electrical components and automotive parts due to its durability, high resistance to temperature, and excellent mechanical properties. The growing industrialization in developing regions further propels the market expansion.

